# Proxy List for GE Login Bot
# 1 proxy per line
# Supported formats:
#   host:port                    (HTTP proxy, no auth)
#   user:pass@host:port          (HTTP proxy with auth)
#   socks5://host:port           (SOCKS5 proxy)
#   socks5://user:pass@host:port (SOCKS5 proxy with auth)
#
# Tips:
# - Use Thai residential proxies for best results (ge.exe.in.th is Thai server)
# - Each parallel worker gets assigned a proxy round-robin
# - Lines starting with # are ignored
#
# Example:
# 203.150.100.1:8080
# user:pass@proxy-th.example.com:3128
# socks5://103.42.57.1:1080
